License: MIT
Description: # Github Info
        
        Show GitHub information on Git pre-push or on demand
        
        ### Requirements
        
        - Python >= 3.6
        
        ### Setup
        
        ```
        pip3 install github-info
        ```
        
        ### Usage
        
        #### 1. Configure the tool
        
        ```
        github-info configure
        ```
        
        #### 2. Use it
        
        ```
        github-info
        ```
        
        ![demo](demo.png)
        
